inline
509{
510 //perpendicular distance of point (x³,y³) = (Ax³ + By³ + C)/Sqrt(A² + B²)
511 //see http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Perpendicular_distance
512 double A = static_cast<double>(ln1.y - ln2.y);

514 double C = A * ln1.x + B * ln1.y;
515 C = A * pt.x + B * pt.y - C;
